In Serie A, Siena appoints former Sampdoria boss Giuseppe Iachini as their new coach after dismissing Serse Cosmi. Also Sampdoria sacks coach Ciro Ferrara after five months in charge on and replaces him with former Lazio and Palermo boss Delio Rossi. (ESPN) (UEFA)In the 2012–13 Fußball-Bundesliga, Bayern Munich wins their 23rd Bundesliga title with a record six games to spare. (UEFA) (Goal.com) (BBC)